### presigned 업로드 (로그인 후 accessToken 사용)
POST {{baseUrl}}/uploads/presign
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "purpose": "POST",
  "contentType": "image/jpeg",
  "fileName": "sample.jpg"
}

### S3 객체 조회 (브라우저/img src)
GET {{baseUrl}}/media?key=posts/1/sample-uuid.jpg
